column7: ['1', '6-Alpha–Linked Maltotriose is Pullulan (Pullulan is the INCI Name)', ' a molecule that', ' just after the application on the skin', ' forms a network at skin surface that is responsible for the immediate shrinking and recompacting effect', ' with subsequent immediate lifting effect. However', ' Pullulan can also be absorbed by the skin and reach the dermis. Its absorption and the reaching of the dermis is promoted by 3 enhancers', ' belonging to the Patent on Labo Skin Technology No. 711 466', ' namely Pentylene Glycol', ' Decylene Glycol', ' Caprylyl Glycol. The Absorption Test conducted by means of Franz Cells (Report E. Ex07-MS04 2016/1896 dated 28/07/2016) showed an overall absorption percentage of Pullulan', ' in both epidermis and dermis', ' equal to 70.5%. The portion of Pullulan that reaches the dermis binds to dermal collagen forming a supporting scaffold that restores tissues’ firmness and compactness for a long time. This is the “”mechanical”” effect in the medium and long term', ' which is added to the medium and long term effect performed by the molecules playing a dermo-cosmetic “”biological”” activity', ' that work synergistically on the structures of the dermis (Glycine', ' Proline', ' Alanine; Tripeptide-10 Citrulline; DMAE; 3-Aminopropane Sulfonic Acid; Acetyl Tetrapeptide-2).']

column2: Fillerina Labo Facial Lifting Cream - Grade 1 1.7 oz
column7: ['1', '6-Alpha–Linked Maltotriose is Pullulan (Pullulan is the INCI Name)', ' a molecule that', ' just after the application on the skin', ' forms a network at skin surface that is responsible for the immediate shrinking and recompacting effect', ' with subsequent immediate lifting effect. However', ' Pullulan can also be absorbed by the skin and reach the dermis. Its absorption and the reaching of the dermis is promoted by 3 enhancers', ' belonging to the Patent on Labo Skin Technology No. 711 466', ' namely Pentylene Glycol', ' Decylene Glycol', ' Caprylyl Glycol. The Absorption Test conducted by means of Franz Cells (Report E. Ex07-MS04 2016/1896 dated 28/07/2016) showed an overall absorption percentage of Pullulan', ' in both epidermis and dermis', ' equal to 70.5%. The portion of Pullulan that reaches the dermis binds to dermal collagen forming a supporting scaffold that restores tissues’ firmness and compactness for a long time. This is the “”mechanical”” effect in the medium and long term', ' which is added to the medium and long term effect performed by the molecules playing a dermo-cosmetic “”biological”” activity', ' that work synergistically on the structures of the dermis (Glycine', ' Proline', ' Alanine; Tripeptide-10 Citrulline; DMAE; 3-Aminopropane Sulfonic Acid; Acetyl Tetrapeptide-2).']

column7: ['1', '6-Alpha–Linked Maltotriose is Pullulan (Pullulan is the INCI Name)', ' a molecule that', ' just after the application on the skin', ' forms a network at skin surface that is responsible for the immediate shrinking and recompacting effect', ' with subsequent immediate lifting effect. However', ' Pullulan can also be absorbed by the skin and reach the dermis. Its absorption and the reaching of the dermis is promoted by 3 enhancers', ' belonging to the Patent on Labo Skin Technology No. 711 466', ' namely Pentylene Glycol', ' Decylene Glycol', ' Caprylyl Glycol. The Absorption Test conducted by means of Franz Cells (Report E. Ex07-MS04 2016/1896 dated 28/07/2016) showed an overall absorption percentage of Pullulan', ' in both epidermis and dermis', ' equal to 70.5%. The portion of Pullulan that reaches the dermis binds to dermal collagen forming a supporting scaffold that restores tissues’ firmness and compactness for a long time. This is the “”mechanical”” effect in the medium and long term', ' which is added to the medium and long term effect performed by the molecules playing a dermo-cosmetic “”biological”” activity', ' that work synergistically on the structures of the dermis (Glycine', ' Proline', ' Alanine; Tripeptide-10 Citrulline; DMAE; 3-Aminopropane Sulfonic Acid; Acetyl Tetrapeptide-2).']
